data.name: GetDistrictbyId
data.value: Select District from [UnicoVehicle].[country].[District] where DeletedDate is null and DistrictId = @districtId

data.name: GetCompanybyId
data.value: Select CompanyName from [UnicoVehicle].[company].[Company] where DeletedDate is null and CompanyId = @companyId

data.name: GetInsuranceCompanybyId
data.value: Select InsuranceCompany from [UnicoVehicle].[insurance].[InsuranceCompany] where DeletedDate is null and InsuranceCompanyId = @insuranceCompanyId

data.name: GetStatebyId
data.value: Select State from [UnicoVehicle].[country].[State] where DeletedDate is null and StateId = @stateId

data.name: GetShowroombyId
data.value: Select CompanyId, DistrictId, ShowroomName from [UnicoVehicle].[company].[Showroom] where DeletedDate is null and ShowroomId = @showroomId
